{"word":"μετοίχομαι","slug":"μετοίχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μετοίχομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-οιχήσομαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to have gone after, to have gone in quest of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to seek for</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>with hostile intent, <i>to pursue</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to have gone among</i> or <i>through</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><i>to have gone with</i> <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}